{"tid":2317080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴士情殺案︱工程師謀殺女友罪成 父裁決前感茫然：依家唯有希望個仔係有問題","createTime":"2020-12-08T10:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T11:05:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":136,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb2439e16e7c9bc0fd5fd91dd5d0e5974190141","tid":2317080,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"本案審期長達37天，較預計超出一倍有多，但公眾席上那位滿臉皺紋、頭髮花白的中年男子從沒缺席。他是被告吳欣鍵眼中的嚴父。籍貫潮州、在街市當菜販的吳爸爸，自孻仔被羈押後，三年來不辭勞苦，每天從觀塘寓所前往荔枝角或赤柱探望。滿心歡喜等待大學畢業的兒子步上康莊大道，最終卻傳來噩耗；為官司耗盡積蓄，更欠下10多萬元。本來望子成龍的吳爸爸，聆訊期間雙眼佈滿紅筋、帶著嘆息的口吻說：「依家唯有希望個仔係有問題，早啲出嚟。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/FAXGIGN53NALHET654MMYTZARU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FFAXGIGN53NALHET654MMYTZARU%2F&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=43c625d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FFAXGIGN53NALHET654MMYTZARU%2F&h=5ce7bc44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/FAXGIGN53NALHET654MMYTZARU/</a>"},{"pid":"0dfe5d382abea1937d82e4bc397300e8d0e87496","tid":2317080,"uid":79117,"like":95,"dislike":8,"score":87,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a39cfbfe17f3f609b15a102a6e64134f282b4dc","tid":2317080,"uid":231480,"like":49,"dislike":9,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"近期啲情殺案判決，更加令我唔信任愛情<br />\n人嘅愛情係永遠最唔信得過"},{"pid":"253d8a523475de8f25525a7f5987420471674199","tid":2317080,"uid":37796,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0a39cfbfe17f3f609b15a102a6e64134f282b4dc","tid":2317080,"uid":231480,"like":49,"dislike":9,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"近期啲情殺案判決，更加令我唔信任愛情<br />\n人嘅愛情係永遠最唔信得過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:06:21.000Z","msg":"叫雞都會中性病"},{"pid":"f06c82e60fb6daa2667260e205ae1b8e0fb48642","tid":2317080,"uid":141782,"like":188,"dislike